    "description": "Condition → best-practice medication options for the doctor/pharmacist teaching loop. Drugs drawn from the NCLEX-familiar core formulary; doses are CONSERVATIVE ADULT LOWER-LIMIT STARTING doses (peds entries weight-based) — the simulated doctor recommends exactly one entry (seeded-random primary, escalating to alternatives), the simulated pharmacist applies instructor-set availability. Edit freely: this file is the single source of truth; the AI never invents a drug or dose beyond it.",
